INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('197', '基建概况', '<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 23pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:华文中宋;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n宋体\">攀枝花学院改革开放以来学校后勤改革与发展成果总结<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:华文中宋;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n宋体\">（<span lang=\"EN-US\">1983-2018</span>）</span><samp><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></samp></p><p class=\"MsoBodyTextIndent2\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-left: 27.1pt; text-indent: 0cm; line-height: 23pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:黑体;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal\">一、学院后勤改革基本概况<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyTextIndent2\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 23pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">1983</span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">年，学校成立总务科、基建科，负责学校基建和后勤服务保障工作<span lang=\"EN-US\">; 1988</span>年学校将行政处划分为总务处、基建环保处，<span lang=\"EN-US\">1999</span>年基建环保处更名基建处。<span lang=\"EN-US\">2001</span>年设立后勤管理处，撤消总务处和劳动服务公司，<span lang=\"EN-US\">2004</span>年成立建设规划处<span lang=\"EN-US\">;2010</span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span>月撤销后勤服务总公司<span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span>成立后勤产业集团公司<span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span>撤销基本建设规划处<span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span>成立后勤管理处<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>负责学校后勤和基建管理工作。<span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span>年后勤改革，在原后勤总公司的基础上组建了后勤产业集团公司，后勤管理和后勤服务保障工作职能剥离，实行甲乙方运行模式。<span lang=\"EN-US\">2017</span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span>学校后勤改革<span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span>撤销后勤产业集团公司<span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span>成立攀大科技产业有限责任公司<span lang=\"EN-US\">.2018</span>年后勤改革<span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span>完成保障、服务、经营分离。目前学校后勤工作包括保障服务和基本建设两部分，后勤系统共有职工<span lang=\"EN-US\">200</span>余人，承担了学校餐饮供给管理、学生公寓管理、公共楼宇管理、水电供应、环境保洁与绿化、卫生防疫及校园规划、工程建设、维护维修等工作。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyTextIndent2\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 23pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:黑体;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">二、认真贯彻落实全国和四川省高校后勤社会化改革工作会议精神，解放思想，转变观念，增强改革意识<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyTextIndent2\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-left: 0cm; line-height: 23pt;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">（一）<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">攀枝花学院党政领导高度重视</span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">后勤社会化改革</span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">，在全校职工大会、全校中层干部会议、校长办公会、党委常委会等<span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span>及时传达贯彻全国高校后勤社会化改革工作会议精神<span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span>并定期不定期召开学校党委、行政和后勤综合改革领导小组会议，及时制定进一步巩固分离成果，深化后勤工作实施意见，专题研究落实改革措施。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyTextIndent2\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-left: 0cm; line-height: 23pt;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">（二）<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">师生是学校的主体，在后勤社会化改革中，我校强化“育人为本，服务至上”的观念，始终坚持“三服务，两育人”服务宗旨不动摇，提升全校师生员工对后勤服务质量、服务水平、服务能力的认可度。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyTextIndent2\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-left: 0cm; line-height: 23pt;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">（三）<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">在改革中明确后勤服务高标准、高起点、高要求的工作目标。坚持为学校教学、科研工，师生员工生活提供优质的后勤服务。不断满足学校建设与发展的需求；不断满足学校教学、科研、师生员工对后勤服务高效率、高质量和高水平的要求；不断在全校形成后勤社会化改革良好的氛围。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyTextIndent2\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 23pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:黑体;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">三、推进运行机制转换，进一步巩固改革，积极落实各项改革措施 <span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyTextIndent2\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-left: 0cm; line-height: 23pt;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">（一）<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">积极推进人事分配制度改革<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyTextIndent2\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 23pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">2018</span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">年，将原属于后勤产业集团公司所属环境服务中心、物业服务中心、水电服务中心、学生公寓服务中心、食堂服务中心<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>个服务性实体重新整合、优化职能结构，分为管理、专业技术、工勤三类岗位，新组建成立校园管理科、物业管理中心、膳食科、学生公寓中心，完成干部聘任工作。同时，注重员工的职业能力、岗位胜任度，积极推进外聘人员再聘用工作。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyTextIndent2\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-left: 0cm; line-height: 23pt;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">（二）<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">积极转换服务运行机制<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyTextIndent2\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 35.85pt; line-height: 23pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">、根据工作特点和服务需要，学校成立物业管理公司，负责学校第二家属区物业管理工作。支持并鼓励其积极参与校外物业服务的投标工作，拓展服务对象、服务层次，取得了良好的经济效益和社会效益。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyTextIndent2\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 35.85pt; line-height: 23pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">、通过公开招标方式，将原属于水电服务中心的维修工作、环境中心的绿化养护、施工工作剥离，交予专业施工单位实施。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:楷体_GB2312;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 33.75pt; line-height: 23pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:楷体_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体\">（三）加强规章制度建设，规范管理<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 35.1pt; line-height: 23pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;letter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">为保障后勤社会化改革工作正常运行，做到后勤工作高标准、规范管理，集团根据管理工作需要，建立了一系列规章制度和管理制度，保证各项工作顺利进行。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"letter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyTextIndent2\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 23pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:黑体;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">四、打造环境优美、卫生整洁的特色校园，让美丽校园环境成为宣传展示学校的一张重要名片。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 35.1pt; line-height: 23pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;letter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">学校立足于建设一个现代化、生态化、地域化的校园，在满足功能需求的基础上，对原有校园规划构思，进行更新、改造和扩建，基本建成一个随时空动态变化、具有浓郁亚热带风格的生态校园。一是规划营造多层次的交流空间，通过课堂内外交流环境的潜移默化，促进学生全面素质的提高。二是充分利用校区地形、地貌、人工湖、边坡等，打造高雅、有文化氛围、有活力的校园环境。建成了中华礼仪墙、科技文化墙，文化雕塑等特色景观，精心设置好校园的每一个角落，突出校区文化的建设与沉淀。三是结合攀西的地域文化，以地方材质表达大学校园的地域精神。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"letter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 35.1pt; line-height: 23pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;letter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">学校现有绿地面积</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"letter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">645</span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nletter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">亩，绿化覆盖率达</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"letter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">51.2%</span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nletter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">，先后荣获攀枝花市“绿化单位”、“园林式单位”、“绿化先进集体”和四川省“城市绿化先进单位”、“园林式单位”等荣誉称号。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"letter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyTextIndent2\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 23pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:黑体;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">五、提供平价、优质、多元的餐饮服务，让师生吃得好，吃得放心。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 35.1pt; line-height: 23pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;letter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">学校有学生食堂</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"letter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nletter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">个，总建筑面积</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"letter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">1.754</span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nletter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">万平方米，餐饮从业人员</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"letter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">300</span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nletter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">余人，餐桌</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"letter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">1339</span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nletter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">张，可同时满足</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"letter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">16000</span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nletter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">余名师生的用餐需求。一是建立健全餐饮服务与食品安全工作制度，优化工作流程，按照食药监督部门的要求，逐步推行量化分级管理、强化日常监督（价格、质量）。二是做好食堂基础设施设备建设，明厨亮灶，并为师生提供干净舒适的就餐环境。三是优化校园餐饮供给服务格局，督促各食堂定期开展菜品创新，促进餐饮服务质量提升。四是连续举办校园美食节，积极倡导绿色、健康、安全、营养的饮食观念，不断增强餐饮服务机构与师生间的沟通联系。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"letter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyTextIndent2\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 23pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:黑体;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">六、建设管理规范、安全文明、整洁温馨的学生公寓，让宿舍有“家”的氛围<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 35.1pt; line-height: 23pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;letter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">学生公寓有宿舍</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"letter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">3524</span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nletter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">间，床位</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"letter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">16303</span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nletter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">个，总建筑面积</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"letter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">13.98</span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nletter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">万平方米。一是注重规范标准建设。公寓服务工作建立了详细的工作流程和实施标准，从源头上保障了管理制度化、服务标准化、操作规范化。是强调人性化的服务。开通公寓服务微信平台，及时处理水电维修等服务申请并快速处理；针对攀枝花高温干旱气候特征，在学生宿舍楼顶加装智能控制喷淋系统进行人工辅助降温、有效改善同学们在高温天气下的体表感受。三是重视公寓文化建设。组织校园文化进公寓，学生党团组织进公寓，在公寓设置时政宣传栏、学生自习区域营造文化氛围，不断推动包括制度文化、行为文化、“家”文化等公寓文化的熏陶作用。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"letter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyTextIndent2\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 23pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:黑体;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">七、尽心做好水电供给、卫生防疫、公共楼宇物业服务等工作，为师生提供舒适的学习生活空间。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 35.1pt; line-height: 23pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;letter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">做好卫生保洁、水电维护维修、公共楼宇管理和隐患排查等工作，积极开展节能降耗，创建节约型校园，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"letter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nletter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">年水电消耗下降</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"letter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">8%</span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nletter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">；近年来投入维修资金约</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"letter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">3100</span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nletter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">万元实施校内基建维修维护项目</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"letter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">349</span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nletter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">项。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"letter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">2016-2017</span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nletter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">年度，利用假期处理公共楼宇屋面防水</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"letter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">14400</span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nletter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">㎡，墙面粉刷</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"letter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">69000</span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nletter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">㎡。引入专业消毒消杀公司，定期对学生寝室、食堂等校内公共环境进行卫生防疫处理；督促校卫生所做好常见疾病数据收集及整理并开展针对性的医疗服务工作，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"letter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nletter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">年卫生所共诊治门诊患者</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"letter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">10000</span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nletter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">余人次。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"letter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyTextIndent2\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 23pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:黑体;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">八、贯彻落实产教融合、转型发展战略，积极推进应用型人才培养平台建设<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 35.1pt; line-height: 23pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;letter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">学校高度重视各类教学科研平台建设，十二五期间，先后建成钒钛中试基地、干热河谷特色生物资源研发中心、交通与汽车工程学院实训大楼、医学实验大楼等。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"letter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nletter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">年，学校成功争取到中央专项及配套资金</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"letter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">14000</span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nletter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">万元，立项建设攀西战略资源开发产教融合实训基地，项目总建筑面积</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"letter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">33999</span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nletter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">平方米</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"letter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nletter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">购置设备</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"letter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">1000</span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nletter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">余台套</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"letter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nletter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\">项目的建成将有力地支持学校应用转型发展，更好地服务于攀西资源综合利用开发。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"letter-spacing:-.2pt;mso-font-kerning:8.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyTextIndent2\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 23pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:黑体;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">九、进一步深化后勤改革应关注的问题<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 28.05pt; line-height: 23pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;\r\nfont-family:楷体_GB2312\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:楷体_GB2312\">、后勤管理处外聘员工实行竞聘上岗、目标管理，效益优先、兼顾公平。取消原实行的校内津贴和奖酬金分配办法，以效益、岗位、目标考核、贡献大小相结合，分步实行企业化方式的员工年工资制分配。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 28.05pt; line-height: 23pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;\r\nfont-family:楷体_GB2312\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:楷体_GB2312\">、要加强队伍素质建设，通过各种培训等方式，大力提高干部员工的文化、专业技术、现代管理、行业服务的整体水平。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyTextIndent2\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 23pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:黑体;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">十、下一步的工作<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 28.05pt; line-height: 23pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;\r\nfont-family:楷体_GB2312\">1. </span><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:\r\n楷体_GB2312\">后勤保障信息化建设。结合数字化校园建设，积极开展智能教室、智慧餐饮、智慧公寓等智慧后勤建设，实现校园服务管理模式的转型升级，为师生提供更好的服务，助力校园文化建设、达到后勤育人的良好效果。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-indent: 0cm;\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 28.05pt; line-height: 23pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;\r\nfont-family:楷体_GB2312\">2. </span><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:\r\n楷体_GB2312\">文化后勤建设。进一步深化后勤综合改革，推动人文后勤、诚信后勤、责任后勤、效率后勤建设，以文化后勤建设为抓手，不断提升后勤保障服务品质。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p></div>\r\n                            \r\n                            \r\n                            \r\n                            \r\n                            \r\n                            \r\n                            \r\n                            ', '2018-12-14 16:37:07', null, '2', '15', '92', '1', '1');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('201', '服务指南', '<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: 宋体;\">做好保障服务工作、助推应用型人才培养</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: 宋体;\">一、后勤管理处简介</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 24pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">后勤管理处是直接隶属于攀枝花学院的服务性质的部门。后勤管理处的可以简单的概括为三服务、两育人。三服务可以概括为为教学、科研、管理工作服务，为学生学习生活和健康成长成才服务，为人才培养和学校事业发展服务。两育人为通过加强自身建设、增强保障能力、提高服务质量实现服务育人；通过完善基础设施、优化空间布局、提升环境质量实现环境育人。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: 宋体;\">二、后勤管理处基本职务</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, sans-serif;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、保障服务</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left: 63pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -21pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, sans-serif;\">1)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">食堂管理</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left: 63pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -21pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, sans-serif;\">2)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">学生公寓</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left: 63pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -21pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, sans-serif;\">3)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">水电供应</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left: 63pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -21pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, sans-serif;\">4)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">公共楼宇管理</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left: 63pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -21pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, sans-serif;\">5)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">环境保洁与绿化</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left: 63pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -21pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, sans-serif;\">6)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">公共卫生防疫</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, sans-serif;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、基本建设</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left: 63pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -21pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, sans-serif;\">1)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: 宋体;\">校园规划</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left: 63pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -21pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, sans-serif;\">2)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">工程建设</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left: 63pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -21pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, sans-serif;\">3)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">维护维修</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, sans-serif;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、工作特色</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left: 66pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -21pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, sans-serif;\">1)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">提供平价、优质、高效、便捷的餐饮服务；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left: 66pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -21pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, sans-serif;\">2)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">建设管理规范、安全文明、整洁舒适、绿色和谐的学生公寓；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left: 66pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -21pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, sans-serif;\">3)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">卫生保洁和公共卫生防疫；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left: 66pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -21pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, sans-serif;\">4)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">加快教学科研生活平台等保障条件建设；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left: 66pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -21pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, sans-serif;\">5)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">分步实施校园绿化美化工程，为师生提供优美的学习生活环境；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left: 66pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -21pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, sans-serif;\">6)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">做好校内基建维修维护工作。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: 宋体;\">三、工作目标</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 24pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">进一步深化后勤综合改革，以文化后勤为抓手，推动人文后勤、法制后勤、责任后勤、效率后勤建设，健全后勤服务标准，不断提升后勤保证服务的层次与品味。</span></p></div>\r\n                            ', '2018-12-13 09:43:04', null, '2', '5', '96', '1', '1');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('240', '《关于成立北苑业主委员会筹备组的通知》', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">北苑业主：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin\">大家好！为了实现北苑的自治管理，加强与广大业主的联系与沟通，方便业主实现与物业对北苑的共建和管理，共同推进北苑校区的物业管理与服务水平，按照《业主委员会选举办法》的相关要求，攀枝花学院后勤处与北苑物业部倡议，组建“北苑业主委员会筹备组”：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin\">现特向广大业主征荐业主委员会筹备组人选，有意向参与的业主、推荐筹备组成员的业主至“北苑物业办公室”（职工之家</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">楼）报名，欢迎广大北苑业主参与到小区的建设当中来，共同建设和谐美丽的北苑校区！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"right\" style=\"text-align:right\"><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">攀枝花学院后勤管理处</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"right\" style=\"text-align:right\"><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">北苑物业部</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n                            \r\n                        ', '2018-12-08 11:04:06', null, '11', '1', '111', '1', '1');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('241', '学生公寓管理制度', '学生公寓管理制度', '2018-12-23 20:21:51', 'file/news/b6cbd_20181022-学生公寓管理制度.doc', '13', '9', '103', '1', '1');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('242', '学生膳食监督委员会', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">简介</span></b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">：攀枝花学院学生膳食监督委员会，前身为学生伙食管理委员会（简称攀大伙管会）成立于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">2004</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">9</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">月，挂靠于攀枝花学院后勤处，膳食科负责具体指导工作。是调解学生与学现食堂关系的桥梁，是代表和维护全校学生正当权益的自律性组织。以“服务同学，锻炼自我，参与伙食民主管理，促进伙食水平提高，反映广大同学心声”为宗旨；以“合理公正，求真务实”为会训；以“收集学生对食堂的意见与要求，协助处理学生与食堂的矛盾”为工作内容；以“维护师生正当权益，监督保障校园饮食安全，促进我校文明就餐风气的形成”为根本；从同学中来，到同学中去，致力于建设攀大和谐校园。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">工作流程</span></b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">：固定时间在</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">食堂执勤点执勤——接受学生对食堂的投诉及建议——执勤人员受理其投诉和建议——每周指导老师将这一周的反映情况反馈给各个食堂负责人——各个食堂针对各种问题加以改进。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">工作职责<span lang=\"EN-US\">:</span></span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:\r\nZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">代表广大学生利益、参与学生饮食服务管理工作、协调学生和各个食堂之间的关系、优化各个食堂的饭菜质量；设立食堂服务质量监督岗，收集和反映学生对食堂安全卫生状况、饭菜质量、服务态度等方面所提出的意见和建议；宣传并提倡文明就餐、维持就餐秩序、协助解决就餐矛盾，为学生提供一个安全，卫生，和谐，明亮的就餐环境。</span>', '2018-12-23 20:21:41', 'file/news/b5832_学生膳食监督委员会.docx', '15', '9', '72', '1', '1');
