INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('249', '物业服务中心配电室安全操作规程', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:22.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">物业服务中心配电室安全操作规程</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:22.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:30.0pt;text-indent:-30.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n-2.5;line-height:125%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n10.0pt;line-height:125%\">&nbsp; 1</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:125%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、操作电工必须具备必要的电工知识，熟悉安全操作规程，熟悉供电系统和配电室各种设备的性能和操作方法，并具备在异常情况下采取措施的能力。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:125%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:125%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:125%\">&nbsp; 2</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:125%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、操作电工要有高度的工作责任心，严格执行值班巡视制度。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:125%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:35.0pt;text-indent:-35.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n-2.5;line-height:125%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:\r\n125%\">&nbsp; 3</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:125%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、不论高压设备带电与否，操作人员不得单人移开或越过遮栏直接工作。若有必要移遮栏时，必须有监护人在场，并符合设备不停电时的安全距离。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:125%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:35.0pt;text-indent:-35.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n-2.5;line-height:125%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:\r\n125%\">&nbsp; 4</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:125%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">．雷雨天气需要巡视室外高压设备时，应穿绝缘鞋，并不得靠近避雷器与避雷针。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:125%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:125%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:125%\">&nbsp; 5</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:125%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">．巡视配电装置，进出高压室，必须随手将门锁好。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:125%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:35.0pt;text-indent:-35.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n-2.5;line-height:125%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:\r\n125%\">&nbsp; 6</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:125%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、停电拉闸必须按照油开关</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:125%\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nline-height:125%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">或负荷开关等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:125%\">)</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nline-height:125%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、负荷侧刀闸、母线侧刀闸的顺序依次操作。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:125%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:35.0pt;text-indent:-35.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n-2.5;line-height:125%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:\r\n125%\">&nbsp; 7</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:125%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、用绝缘棒分合高压刀闸或经传动分合高压刀闸和油开关，都应戴绝缘手套。雨天操作室外高压设备时，应穿绝缘靴。雷电时禁止进行倒闸操作。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:125%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n-2.5;line-height:125%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:\r\n125%;letter-spacing:.2pt\">&nbsp; 8</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:125%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;letter-spacing:.2pt\">、带电装卸熔断器时，应戴防护眼镜和绝缘手套，必要时使用绝缘夹钳，并站在绝缘垫上。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:125%;letter-spacing:.2pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:35.0pt;text-indent:-35.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n-2.5;line-height:125%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:\r\n125%\">&nbsp; 9</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:125%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、电气设备停电后，在未拉开刀闸和做好安全措施以前，应视有电不得触及设备和进入遮栏，以防突然来电。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:125%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:35.0pt;text-indent:-35.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n-2.5;line-height:125%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:\r\n125%\">&nbsp; 10</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:125%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、施工和检修需要停电时，操作人员应按照工作要求做好安全措施，包括停电、检电、装设遮栏和悬挂标示牌、接临时地线，会同工作负责人现场检查确认无电，并交待附近带电设备位置和注意事项，方可开始工作。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:125%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:35.0pt;text-indent:-35.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n-2.5;line-height:125%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:\r\n125%\">&nbsp; 11</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:125%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、高压设备带电工作时，距离操作人员工作正常活动范围小于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:125%\">O.35</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:125%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">米必须停电；距离大于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:125%\">0.35</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:125%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">米但小于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:125%\">0.7</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:125%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">米设备，必须在与带电部分不小于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:125%\">0.35</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:125%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">的距离处设牢固的临时遮栏，否则必须停电。带电部分在操作人员的后面或两侧无采取可靠措施者也必须停电。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:125%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:35.0pt;text-indent:-35.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n-2.5;line-height:125%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:\r\n125%\">&nbsp; 12</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:125%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、停电时必须切断各回路可能来电的电源。不能只拉开油开关进行工作，而必须拉开刀闸，使各回路至少有一个明显的断开点。变压器与电压互感器必须从高低压两侧断开。电压互感器的一、二次熔断器都要取下。油开关的操作电源要断开。刀闸的操作把手要锁住。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:125%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:35.0pt;text-indent:-35.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n-2.5;line-height:125%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:\r\n125%\">&nbsp; 13</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:125%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、验电时必须用电压等级合适并且合格的验电器，在检修设备时出线两侧分别验电。验电前应先在有电设备上试验证明验电器良好。高压设备验电必须戴绝缘手套、穿绝缘鞋。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:125%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:125%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:125%\">&nbsp; 14</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:125%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、在电容器回路上工作时必须将电容器逐个放电。放电后接地。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:125%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:42.0pt;text-indent:-42.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n-3.0;line-height:125%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:\r\n125%\">&nbsp; 15</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:125%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、在一经合闸即可送电到工作地点的开关和刀闸操作把手，都应悬挂“禁止合闸，有人工作”的标示牌。工作地点两旁和对面的带电设备遮栏上和禁止通行的过道上悬挂“止步、高压危险”的标示牌。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:125%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:35.0pt;text-indent:-35.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n-2.5;line-height:125%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:\r\n125%\">&nbsp; 16</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:125%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、线路或用户检修要求停电时，操作人员应采取安全措施，然后通知对方负责人开始工作并进行登记。工作结束后必须接到原负责人通知方可恢复送电。严禁约时停、送电。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:125%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:35.0pt;text-indent:-35.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n-2.5;line-height:125%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:\r\n125%\">&nbsp; 17</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:125%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、在带电设备附近工作时，必须设专人监护。带电设备只能在操作人员的前面或一侧，否则应停电进行。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:125%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:35.0pt;text-indent:-35.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n-2.5;line-height:125%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:\r\n125%\">&nbsp; 18</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:125%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、低压回路停电检修时应断开电源，取下熔断器。在刀闸操作把手上挂“禁止合闸，有人工作”的标示牌。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:125%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:35.0pt;text-indent:-35.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n-2.5;line-height:125%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:\r\n125%\">&nbsp; 19</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:125%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、低压设备带电工作时，应设专人监护。工作中要戴工作帽，穿长袖衣服，戴绝缘手套，穿绝缘鞋，使用有绝缘柄的工具，并站在干燥的绝缘物上进行工作。相邻的带电部分，应用绝缘板<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.4pt\">料隔开。严禁使用锉刀、金属尺和带有金属物的毛刷、毛掸工具。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:125%;letter-spacing:-.4pt\">&nbsp; </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:125%\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:35.05pt;mso-para-margin-left:1.34gd;\r\ntext-indent:-21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:-1.5;line-height:125%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:125%\">20</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:125%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、在带电的电流互感器二次回路上工作时，要严防电流互感器二次侧开路产生高电压。断开电流回路时，必须使用短路线在电流互感器二次的专用端子上短路。严禁用导线缠绕。工作中不得将回路的永久接地点断开。工作时必须有专人监护，使用绝缘工具，并站在绝缘垫上。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:125%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n-1.5;line-height:125%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:\r\n125%\">&nbsp; 21</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:125%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、发生人身触电事故和火灾事故，操作人员应立即断开有关设备</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:125%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.0pt;mso-para-margin-left:2.0gd;\r\ntext-indent:14.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:1.0;line-height:125%\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:125%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">的电源，以便进行抢救。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:125%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:35.05pt;mso-para-margin-left:1.34gd;\r\ntext-indent:-21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:-1.5;line-height:125%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:125%\">22</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:125%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、电器设备发生火灾时，应该用二氧化碳灭火器或</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:125%\">1211</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:125%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">灭火器<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.4pt\">扑救。变压器着火时，只有在全部停电后才能用泡沫灭火器扑救。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:125%;letter-spacing:-.4pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.5pt;line-height:25%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:25%;letter-spacing:-.4pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;line-height:25%\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.5pt;line-height:25%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:25%\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:287.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:20.5\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">物业服务中心</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:301.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:21.5\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">2018</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">9</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', '2018-12-23 20:22:27', 'file/news/d6a88_物业服务中心配电室安全操作规程.doc', '14', '9', '59', '1', '0');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('250', '物业服务中心配电室安全管理制度', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom:15.6pt;mso-para-margin-bottom:\r\n1.0gd;text-align:center\"><b><span style=\"font-size:22.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">物业服务中心配电室安全管理制度</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:22.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n16.0pt;line-height:150%\">&nbsp; </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">配电室是学校的重点要害部位，设备安全正常运转是教学科研任务能否顺利完成，师生学习和生活秩序是否正常井然的重要保证。同时也关系到学校财产安全和师生员工人身安全。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:24.0pt;text-indent:-24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n-2.0;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">一、变压器、电容器等变、配电装置在运行中发生异常情况不能排除时，应立即停止运行。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:24.0pt;text-indent:-24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n-2.0;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">二、配电室门应加锁，并设置警示标志。对设在建筑物首层配电室的外窗应加装防护栏（网）。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:29.65pt;text-indent:-29.65pt;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n-2.47;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">三、对存在安全隐患的设施设备，维修电工要及时将隐患情况和整改方案上报主管领导，待整改方案批准后立即实施整改，消除安全隐患。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:24.0pt;text-indent:-24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n-2.0;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">四、维修电工须有专业资格证书方可上岗。对配电室进行维修保养作业时应按规定穿戴好防护用品做好安全防护，严格遵守行业操作规范安全操作，防止发生安全事故。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:24.0pt;text-indent:-24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n-2.0;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">五、安装、维修配电设施设备时，要在上级开关悬挂“有人操作、严禁合闸”的标志牌，严格执行安全操作规程并有应急照明装置。学校内维修需停电时，部门负责人下达停电命令，由电工拉闸停电，在明显处挂停电标示牌并由电工守护，维修完毕后由负责人口头通知合闸。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:24.0pt;text-indent:-24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n-2.0;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">六、配电室应配备适用电器灭火的消防器材并存放在便于取用的位置，维修人员应熟知使用方法，严禁将消防器材挪作他用。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:24.0pt;text-indent:-24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n-2.0;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">七、配电室内不得堆放杂物或与工作无关的物品，坚决禁止存放和堆积易燃易爆物品。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">八、变压器的保养、检修应按规定周期进行。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:24.0pt;text-indent:-24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n-2.0;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">九、高、低压变配电装置应在每年寒、暑假各进行一次停电、清扫、检修工作。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n-1.5;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">十、严禁将易燃易爆危险物品带进高低压配电室；配电室内严禁吸烟。工作人员必须熟练使用消防器材。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">十一、严禁非工作人员进入配电室。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n-3.0;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">十二、抄表员来抄表，工作人员应做好配合、复核工作，确保交费及时、准确。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">十三、遇到紧急事故，应快速准确地断电、防止事故扩大</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>', '2018-12-23 20:22:38', 'file/news/cb058_物业服务中心配电室安全管理制度.doc', '14', '9', '34', '1', '0');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('251', '物业服务中心水电突发事件应急处理预案', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 22pt; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">后管处物业中心水电突发事件应急处理预案<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 28pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 28pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">一、<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>停电预案<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 28pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">（一）计划停电<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 28pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">、中心在接到供电部门的停电通知后，应立即告知后管处，同时电话通知食堂、公寓中心、安信物业等，并在学院电子公告栏张贴通知。通知内容应说明停电时间、恢复供电时间，并提醒各单位在停电期间将所有开关予以关闭。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 28pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">、安排电工进行设备看护并准备排除突发故障。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 7.8pt; line-height: 28pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 3</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">、电力恢复时，人工进行相关变电器、分测中心、图书馆、二教楼、第二家属小区总开关合闸操作，并检查有关用电设备是否正常运行。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">（二）突然停电<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: 47.3pt; text-indent: -47.3pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">、局部停电，应先分析故障原因，在<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>小时内排除一般问题；如问题不是维修人员能解决的，应及时与供电部门或相关专业公司联系处理。整个校园停电，物业中心要立即电询供电局派人查巡。如属学院内部供电系统出现问题的（如变压器、电缆线路被盗等），应立即通知电工抢修，力争在最短时间恢复供电，并报告后管处分管领导。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: 42pt; text-indent: -42pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">、通知维修人员前往停电现场及到公共用电设备部位巡查公共电器是否受停电影响，待电力恢复后，维修人员要检查受影响的公共用电设备是否恢复正常运行。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: 42pt; text-indent: -42pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 3</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">、因我校重要用电部门食堂、会堂为双电源供电，如遇其中一条供电线路停电时，维修人员应立即启用备用线路供电；如遇双电源同时停电时，我部门与学校相关部门共同联系电业局派发电车来我校提供供电保障。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 4</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">、当发生低压瞬时跳闸时，要尽快查明故障原因和恢复供电，并做好值班记录。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 15.6pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 5</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">、当发生高压停电故障时，要尽快和供电局取得联系，询问故障原因。高压开关房设专人观察，故障停电时要立即切断电容柜和各分闸开关，做好一切准备工作。送电时要严格按照操作程序进行，送电完毕，维修人员仍需集中在变配电房一段时间，以防再次发生停电故障，并处理送电后可能引发的其他故障。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 27pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">二、停水预案<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 27pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">（一）计划停水<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: 69.55pt; text-indent: -13.7pt; line-height: 27pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">、我部门在接到供水部门的停水通知后，要立即告知后管处，同时电话通知食堂、学生公寓、安信物业等，并在学院电子公告栏张贴通知，通知内容应说明停水时间、恢复供水时间，并提醒各单位在停水期间将所有开关予以关闭。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 27pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">、停水前将我校<span lang=\"EN-US\">800</span>吨蓄水池蓄满水备食堂使用。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 27pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">3</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">、供水恢复时，维修人员检查所有供水主管道是否有断水或漏水情况。各楼栋值班人员检查全体楼栋水管阀门关闭情况。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 7.8pt; text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 27pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">4</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">、如遇停水时间过长，<span lang=\"EN-US\">800</span>吨水池用完，应采取相关措施，如联系消防车、环卫洒水车送水等，确保食堂用水。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 27pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">（二）突然停水<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: 52.5pt; text-indent: -20.5pt; line-height: 28pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">、局部停水，应先分析故障原因，在<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>小时内排除一般问题。如问题不是维修人员能解决的，应及时与水务集团或相关专业公司联系处理。整个校园停水，物业部门要立即电询水务集团派人查巡。如属学院内部供水系统出现问题（如主供水管断裂，主供水阀门故障等），相关单位要立即组织员工进行抢修，力争在最短时间内恢复供水。维修人员无能力解决的，要及时报告后管处分管领导，请其它相关单位协助处理。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 28pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">3</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">、如停水时间过长，<span lang=\"EN-US\">800</span>吨水池用完，要采取相应措施如联系消防车、<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>环卫洒水车送水等，确保食堂用水。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 28pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">4</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">、供水恢复后，检查供水是否正常，同时派人详细巡检供水设备是否<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>恢复正常。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 28pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">三、应急部门联系方式<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 28pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">电力部门：<span lang=\"EN-US\">95598<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 28pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">水务部门：<span lang=\"EN-US\">13908149920<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 28pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">消防部门：<span lang=\"EN-US\">119<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 28pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 32pt; line-height: 28pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\ntab-stops:441.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\ntab-stops:441.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">后勤集团水电中心</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\ntab-stops:441.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2013</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">日</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\ntab-stops:441.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\ntab-stops:441.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>', '2018-12-23 20:22:47', 'file/news/f4231_物业服务中心水电突发事件应急处理预案.doc', '14', '9', '42', '1', '0');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('255', '物业服务中心电梯运行管理细则', '物业服务中心电梯运行管理细则', '2018-12-14 15:15:17', 'file/news/3a132_物业服务中心电梯运行管理细则.doc', '2', '8', '49', '1', '0');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('257', '学生公寓管理制度', '<h2 align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:28.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n2.0;line-height:26.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;tab-stops:center 200.7pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">攀枝花学院学生公寓管理规定<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:28.1pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:26.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">第一章<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>总<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>则<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:26.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">第一条</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">为了加强学生公寓管理，维护学生正常的学习、生活秩序，促进学生公寓高品质的文化建设，将学生公寓建设成为思想政治工作和素质教育的重要育人阵地，使其成为学生“温馨舒适的家园、强身益智的乐园、学习创新的摇篮”。依据《普通高等学校学生管理规定》、《教育部关于切实加强高校学生住宿管理的通知》和《攀枝花学院学生违纪处理办法》，结合我校学生公寓的实际情况，制定本规定。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:26.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">第二条</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">学生公寓管理是学校学生管理工作的重要组成部分，学生公寓服务中心是在后勤管理处领导下负责公寓管理和服务工作的日常办事机构，其主要职责是：负责学生正常的日常管理和服务工作；负责公寓服务中心工作人员的招聘、培训、管理、考核；负责拟订全校学生公寓的分配、调整方案；协调各二级学院参与公寓内的学生管理和寝室文化建设；协助学校相关部门负责对学生公寓进行基建性维修维护、安全保卫、信息与网络管理等事务；完成学校交办的其它任务。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:26.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">第三条</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">公寓成立学生爱心接力协会、公寓协管员，在公寓服务中心的指导下爱心接力协会是从事社会公益性活动的团体，爱心接力协会普及公益思想、提倡社会文明和进步、促进公益事业全面发展为己任，以“携手共助•传递真情”的思想为宗旨。主要是组织和策划爱心活动，同时也从事志愿活动，给同学们一个爱心的平台，让爱心得以传递。公寓协管员是协助楼栋管理员在迎检、迎新、突击加班等时参与到卫生清扫、在发现学生有违规、违纪等行为及发现安全隐患时及时向学生公寓服务中心汇报，对公寓内的好人好事、管理员优秀事迹等进行宣传报道。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:28.1pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:26.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">第二章<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>住宿、退宿、调宿<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:26.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">第四条</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">公寓服务中心在每学年初根据在校学生和房源情况，提出各二级学院学生宿舍的分配和调整方案，报请学生处批准后实施。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:26.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">第五条</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">学生个人的具体入住寝室和床位，由各二级学院统筹安排。学生入住寝室之前应凭各二级学院盖章签发的《攀枝花学院学生公寓住宿卡》，到各公寓值班室领取住宿房间钥匙。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:26.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">第六条</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">学生住宿一旦确定，未经公寓服务中心同意任何单位和个人均不得自行调整。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:26.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">第七条</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">学生毕业、休学、退学或其它原因需办理离校手续者，必须按离校程序要求在规定时限内办结退宿手续；无特殊原因逾期不办结者，将提请保卫处强制执行离校。办理退宿手续按公寓服务中心的具体实施办法执行。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:26.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">第八条</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">在校学生未经批准一律不得在学生公寓外租房住宿。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:26.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">第九条 </span></b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">&nbsp;寒暑假期间，住宿学生原则上应按规定离校，确需继续入住公寓的学生必须按公寓服务中心要求提出书面申请，并办理《出入证》等相关手续，否则公寓服务中心有权强制执行离校。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:26.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">第十条</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">留级、转二级学院、转专业、专升本的学生，原则上应将住宿调整至新到班级宿舍内。二级学院内部调整由二级学院自行负责并报公寓服务中心备案，跨二级学院调整由公寓服务中心协调。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:26.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">第十一条</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">不超过一年的实习，同学在离开公寓时主动到值班室办理离宿登记，返校后经公寓服务中心同意继续入住原处。超过（包括一年）的实习，同学离宿时必须办理退宿手续，实习结束后公寓服务中心不安排住宿。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:28.1pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:26.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">第三章<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>公寓设施设备<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:26.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">第十二条</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">学生公寓内的水电基础设施、床铺、衣柜、桌、凳、网络终端接口等由学校一次性统一配置；床上用品通过学校招标确定供应商，由学生到校后自行购置。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:26.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">第十三条</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">网络配套设施的使用和管理办法参照学校有关规定执行。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:26.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">第十四条</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">所有学生都必须爱护和正确使用公寓配套设施设备，因人为损坏由学生照价赔偿并承担相应责任，情节严重者报请学校给予相应的纪律处分。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:26.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">第十五条</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">公寓服务中心和学校有关部门有责任和义务确保公寓内各种设施设备的完整和正常使用。入住学生有权提出维修、维护要求，发生的费用按责任承担。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:28.1pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:26.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">第四章<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>纪律要求<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:26.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">第十六条</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">学生公寓是学生学习、生活、人际交往和良好行为习惯养成的重要公共场所，任何学生都有自觉遵守学校相应的各项管理规章制度和自觉维护公寓正常秩序的义务。公寓服务中心有权按照学校要求对所有入住公寓的学生进行教育管理，对不服从管理或经教育不改者公寓服务中心可以根据《攀枝花学院学生违纪处理办法》报请学校给予纪律处分。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:26.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">第十七条</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">学校严禁学生在公寓内留宿异性和容许异性留宿；严禁在公寓内赌博、酗酒、打麻将、打架斗殴；严禁在非指定地点张贴标语、广告、海报；严禁违章用电和违章使用电器、燃具和照明用具等；严禁私拉乱接各种线路；严禁存放和使用法定违禁用品；严禁观看、制作、复制、传播和销售非法书刊和音像制品；严禁饲养宠物；严禁存放和兜售营销性物品；严禁卧床吸烟、随地乱扔烟头、燃放烟花爆竹；严禁向窗外丢掷物品；公寓内严禁堆放杂物，不得在公寓内进行“土、木、铁”类加工或制作。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:26.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">第十八条</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">学生应养成良好的公共卫生和个人卫生习惯，保持公共区域和寝室的干净整洁，建立健全寝室值日制度。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:26.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">第十九条</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">学生应遵守公寓作息时间，不早出晚归；遵守供电和输送电视信号时间安排，不无理取闹；遵守集体生活规范，不从事影响他人正常休息和学习的任何活动。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:26.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">第二十条</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">学生应增强自我防范意识，不在寝室内存放现金和贵重物品，贵重物品必须按照公寓服务中心的要求进行保管；未经允许不能擅自进入他人寝室。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:26.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">第二十一条</span></b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\"> 学生应遵守公寓门岗制度，未经允许不得在宿舍内接待和逾期滞留校外来访人员；大宗或贵重物品进出公寓必须接受值班人员检查并办理登记手续。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:26.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">第二十二条</span></b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\"> 学生应遵守学生公寓服务中心有关公寓管理的相关规定。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:28.1pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:26.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">第五章<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>附则<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:26.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">第二十三条</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体;\">本条例</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">从<st1:chsdate isrocdate=\"False\" islunardate=\"False\" day=\"1\" month=\"9\" year=\"2018\" w:st=\"on\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2018</span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>日起</st1:chsdate>执行，凡此前文件规定中有与本规定有矛盾之处，以本规定为准。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:26.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">第二十四条</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">本规定由公寓服务中心负责解释。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>', '2018-12-23 20:30:20', 'file/news/ef271_20181022-学生公寓管理制度.doc', '13', '9', '50', '1', '0');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('258', '微信平台管理办法', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt;font-family:仿宋\">学生公寓服务中心微信平台管理办法<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:29.4pt;mso-char-indent-count:1.96\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:仿宋\">为充分发挥微信平台的对外宣传和信息交流的作用，严格审核微信公众号内容发布，规范平台管理，明确平台的管理职责，规范发布流程及日常管理，特制定本办法。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:仿宋\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;\r\nfont-family:仿宋\">一、日常管理办法<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:29.25pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:仿宋\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;\r\nfont-family:仿宋\">、管理员每日关注平台信息，回复各类咨询问题。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:29.25pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:仿宋\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;\r\nfont-family:仿宋\">、对于投诉、建议等信息，及时上报给刘主任，调查处理后回复处理结果。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:29.25pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:仿宋\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;\r\nfont-family:仿宋\">、及时更新平台各类信息。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:29.25pt\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;\r\nfont-family:仿宋\">二、内容发布流程<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:29.25pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:仿宋\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;\r\nfont-family:仿宋\">、办公室做好信息的收集、整理。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:29.25pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:仿宋\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;\r\nfont-family:仿宋\">、管理员编辑发布的信息。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:29.25pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:仿宋\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;\r\nfont-family:仿宋\">、交由<u><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></u>审核。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:29.25pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:仿宋\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;\r\nfont-family:仿宋\">、审核通过后，发布在微信平台上。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:29.25pt\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;\r\nfont-family:仿宋\">三、信息编辑要求<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:29.25pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:仿宋\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;\r\nfont-family:仿宋\">、内容简明扼要，中心突出。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:29.25pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:仿宋\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;\r\nfont-family:仿宋\">、内容真实、及时，无病句、错别字等。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:29.25pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:仿宋\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;\r\nfont-family:仿宋\">、配图需规格合适、贴合主题。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:29.25pt\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;\r\nfont-family:仿宋\">四、平台的推广<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:29.25pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:仿宋\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;\r\nfont-family:仿宋\">、将微信平台二维码发至楼栋，由管理员在学生寝室推广。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:29.25pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:仿宋\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;\r\nfont-family:仿宋\">、在每篇文章末推送平台二维码。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 29.4pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:仿宋\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:仿宋\">学生公寓服务中心<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n                                \r\n                            ', '2019-02-26 10:14:22', 'file/news/2b86d_公寓中心--微信平台管理办法.docx', '13', '9', '26', '1', '0');

-- ----------------------------
-- Table structure for officeduty
-- ----------------------------
DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `officeduty`;
CREATE TABLE `officeduty` (
  `dept_id` int(10) NOT NULL,
  `duty` text NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`dept_id`),
  UNIQUE KEY `PK_officeDuty_1` (`dept_id`),
  KEY `IX_officeDuty` (`dept_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

-- ----------------------------
-- Records of officeduty
-- ----------------------------
INSERT INTO `officeduty` VALUES ('1', '\r\n                        \r\n                                \r\n                                <p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><font face=\"楷体\" size=\"5\"><b>医疗卫生科工作职责</b></font><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、熟悉中央、省、市有关高校食品安全与公共卫生防疫工作的政策法规，熟悉学校有关管理制度。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、贯彻执行传染病防治法规，落实疫情管理规章制度，做好校内常见病、传染病的防治工作。</span>\r\n<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、负责组织学校公共区域爱卫会卫生检查和考核工作。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、负责全校范围内病媒生物消杀、消毒工作。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、负责新生入学健康体检工作，建立学生健康档案。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、负责开展校内健康教育宣传。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、负责校区内饮用水安全管理。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、负责全校职工慢性病申报、报销工作。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、负责全校计划生育工作。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、负责校区内的零售药品检查工作。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">11</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">、完成领导交办的其他任务。</span><br></p>\r\n                            \r\n                            \r\n                    ');
INSERT INTO `officeduty` VALUES ('2', '\r\n                                <p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\"><b><font size=\"5\">综合科工作职责</font></b></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:42.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:3.0\">\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;\r\nmso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">负责部门日常行政管理工作（公章、公文、档案、数据统计、信息报送、来访接待、工作督办、后勤系统干部大会、部门内部各类会议及相应的纪要，部门各类计划、总结、规划、年鉴等）；后勤文化建设；各类规章制度的建立和完善；后勤信息化建设；部门年度考核工作；部门内部人、财、物的管理及年度预算申报；后勤系统各类人员的聘用、考核及薪酬核算；组织各类后勤物资的采购与入库。</span><br></p>\r\n                            ');
INSERT INTO `officeduty` VALUES ('3', '\r\n                                <p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\"><b><font size=\"5\">工程管理科工作职责</font></b></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、认真贯彻执行国家基本建设的方针、政策、法律和条例；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、根据学校安排，负责与学校有关部门共同编制、管理和执行校园建设总体规划；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、负责学校土地征用、红线管理</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">处理周边关系；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、负责按主管部门要求编制和报送年度基本建设计划；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、负责校外施工企业（未与学校签订施工合同企业）入校施工管理；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、负责建设项目的可行性和必要性研究，编制可行性研究报告，为学校提供决策依据；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、负责建设项目报建手续办理；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、负责建设项目的地质勘察和设计管理；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、负责建设项目的施工管理，确保工程质量；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋\">负责组织建设项目的竣工验收，做好竣工结算工程量、各项签证、竣工图及竣工资料的审核工作</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 24pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">11</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">、</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">完成处领导交办的其他任务。</span><br></p>\r\n                            ');
INSERT INTO `officeduty` VALUES ('4', '\r\n                                <p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\"><b><font size=\"5\">工程经济科工作职责</font></b></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n12.0pt\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、熟悉国家、省市有关高校工程经济活动的政策法规，熟悉学校有关管理制度。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n12.0pt\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、负责组织各类工程招标项目招标文件的拟定、审查及备案工作，负责中标通知书发放，组织中标合同的签定。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n12.0pt\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、负责拟建项目概算金额的核定，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n12.0pt\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、负责将通过竣工验收项目的竣工资料移交审计处办理结算，并做好登记。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n12.0pt\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、负责各类在建、竣工项目工程建设信息的统计，做好各类招投标资料、结算资料的收集、整理及移交。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n12.0pt\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、完成领导临时交办的各项工作。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n                            ');
INSERT INTO `officeduty` VALUES ('11', '\r\n                                <p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\"><font size=\"5\"><b>北苑物业部工作职责</b></font></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、按学校要求，对北苑家属区进行校内物业管理，负责小区内公共设施的零星维修、维护。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、提升北苑环境卫生质量、做好小区楼栋楼道及室外公共区域卫生保洁工作。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、增强家属区绿化、美化效果、对树木按季节进行适宜修建、枯枝处理。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、进行零星小型室外设施维护、维修、报修。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、协助相关部门做好小区内车辆有序停放的指挥、指导、劝导工作。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、制止小区内乱摆摊设点、乱倒乱扔垃圾现象，协调环卫每天进行小区生活垃圾及时清运工作。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、规范小区内小广告、做好小广告清理工作。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、按上级领导要求完成交办的其他工作任务。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">联系方式：</span> &nbsp;<span lang=\"EN-US\">0812</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">—</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3371108<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n                            ');
INSERT INTO `officeduty` VALUES ('12', '\r\n                                \r\n                                \r\n                                \r\n                                <p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\"><b><font size=\"5\">房产科工作职能</font></b></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、负责统筹学校房产资源规划及功能调整；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、负责学校各类行政办公用房和非教学教辅用房管理；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、负责办理学校教职工房屋产权手续；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、为全校教职工住房出售提供政策咨询及服务；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">科长岗位职责：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、负责制定房产科相关规章制度，岗位职责、年度工作计划和工作总结；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nCalibri\">、负责学校公共楼宇统筹规划及功能调整；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nCalibri\">、负责协助教职员工办理相关房屋产权证工作；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nCalibri\">、积极协调相关部门处理好有关房屋产权证办理的历史遗留问题；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nCalibri\">、负责有关房产政策的宣传工作；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、完成领导交办的其他工作。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">科员岗位职责：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、负责学校房产资源规划及功能调整；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、负责非教学教辅用房管理；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、负责学校教职工遗留房产产权的办理；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、负责协助相关部门处理好学校教职工房产相关工作；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、负责学校教职工房改房的买卖审批；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、负责房产政策、信息推送；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"line-height: 15pt;\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、完成领导交办的其他工作。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n                            \r\n                            \r\n                            \r\n                            ');
INSERT INTO `officeduty` VALUES ('13', '\r\n                                \r\n                                \r\n                                \r\n                                \r\n                                \r\n                                <h1 align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:28.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n2.0;line-height:26.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><b style=\"\"><font size=\"5\">公寓服务中心办公室岗位设置</font></b></span></h1><h1 align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28.1pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><b style=\"color: inherit; text-indent: 28.1pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">一、</span></b><span style=\"color: inherit; text-indent: 28.1pt; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体;\">学生公寓服务中心主任<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>名</span></h1><h1 align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:28.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:\r\n2.0;line-height:26.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\">\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">二、学生公寓服务中心副主任<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>名<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">三、学生公寓服务中心办公室主任<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>名（兼学生住宿及工资管理）<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">四、学生公寓服务中心安全管理专干<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>名（兼水电管理）<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">五、学生公寓服务中心卫生管理专干<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>名（兼公众平台管理）<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">六、学生公寓服务中心资产管理专干<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>名（兼库房管理）<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">七、学生公寓服务中心质量监督考核管理专干<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>名（兼数据档案管理）<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 9.9pt; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 26pt;\"><b><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><font size=\"5\">岗位职责</font></span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 26pt;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">第一节<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>学生公寓服务中心主任岗位职责</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">第一条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>在后勤管理处领导下，认真传达、贯彻、执行学校及后勤管理处的有关文件精神和规章制度，并按照中心的实际情况，制定和落实相关的规章制度。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">第二条<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <a name=\"OLE_LINK11\">&nbsp;</a></span>负责学生公寓服务中心规章制度的制定、修改和执行。<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">第三条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>负责学生公寓服务中心的年度工作计划、总结、请示汇报工作。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">第四条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>全面负责中心的人事、财务、物资的管理。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">第五条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>全面负责中心的人事、工资改革。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">第六条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>负责学生公寓服务中心管理人员、治安人员和清洁人员“三支队伍”的建设、教育管理工作。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">第七条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>全面负责中心的安全管理工作。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">第八条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>全面负责中心与学校相关部门、后勤管理处各科室、中心的协调和沟通工作。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">第九条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>完成领导交办的其他工作。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 26pt;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">第二节<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>学生公寓服务中心副主任岗位职责<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">第一条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>在中心主任的领导下，按照主任的指示，具体传达、执行、落实学校及<a name=\"OLE_LINK4\"></a><a name=\"OLE_LINK3\">后勤管理处</a>的有关文件精神和中心的规章制度。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">第二条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>积极配合、协调主任的工作，当好主任的助手和参谋。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">第三条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>负责中心各项规章制度的起草、修改及贯彻落实。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">第四条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>负责公寓中心工作人员的招聘、入职、培训、管理、考核、离职、调岗等相关工作。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">第五条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>组织中心员工认真学习学校及后勤管理处的有关文件精神和中心的规章制度，并协助主任做好员工的思想政治工作。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">第六条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>负责中心的日常、月度、年度考评工作。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">第七条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>负责中心服务质量的落实和监管工作。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">第八条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>负责协调各院<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>系<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>和学生公寓自律委员会（简称：自律会）参与公寓内的学生管理和寝室文化建设。并通过倡导学生自我教育、自我管理和自我服务，不断改善公寓环境，提高公寓文化建设水平。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">第九条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>负责中心的日常管理；负责管理中心公章；负责开出相关证明。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">第十条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>完成领导交办的其他工作。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28.1pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">第三节<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">学生公寓服务中心办公室主任岗位职责<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">第一条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>在学生公寓服务中主任领导下，主持中心办公室的日常行政事务工作。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">第二条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>负责中心对内（对外）发函、申请、报告、通知、工作计划、总结等文件的起草。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">第三条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>负责中心工作记事和会议的组织筹备，并做好会议纪要。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">第四条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>负责管理审核中心考勤的汇总和员工工资的记发工作。各楼栋座机费及公寓其它费用的签字、报销工作。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">第五条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>负责中心来访接待工作。参加中心的常规检查工作。负责办公室的环境卫生工作。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">第六条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>负责中心的宣传工作，审核楼栋宣传栏、信息网页内容制作、更新，把好文字关。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">第七条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>负责院（系）公寓学生管理工作，与各院（系）学生科联系抓好学生晚归和夜不归宿的检查工作，督促学生按时就寝。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">第八条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>负责全院学生床位的调配和安排。<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">第九条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>负责寒、暑假住宿学生数据的统计。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">第十条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>负责学生住宿情况数据系统的维护。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">第十一条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>处理突发事件，关注负责辖区内学生及员工的动态。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">第十二条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>完成学生公寓服务中心主任交办的其它任务。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28.1pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">第四节<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>学生公寓服务中心安全管理岗位职责</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">第一条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>全面负责公寓日常安全工作，巡查各公寓发现问题及时上报，对于公寓的所有安全问题每天定时收集、汇总、上报。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">第二条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>负责学生公寓、有关办公用房及学生活动场所、防火防盗等安全稳定工作。在公寓内开展安全教育活动和安全检查工作，对存在的安全隐患进行整改，确保公寓的安全和稳定。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">第五条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>每天各公寓定时上报人员安全、公物安全存在的问题，整理、汇总上报，并督促处理。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">第三条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>通过网络监督各公寓进出人员动态，发现问题立即上报处理。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">第四条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>定期录入各公寓用水数据，核实、汇总后，需收费的数据报水电中心。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">第五条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>公寓水电表管理，对于不能正常使用的仪表，汇总报有关部门，督促处理。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">第六条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>洗衣机的管理，对于不能正常使用的机器，及时联系相关人员处理。洗衣卡涉及数据、资金交办公室主任处，作好相关记录并存档。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">第七条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>定期组织公寓职工进行安全学习，对突发事件的处理进行培训。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">第八条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>处理突发事件，随时走访学生寝室关注学生及员工的思想动态，对存在的问题上报。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">第九条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>完成学生公寓服务中心主任交办的其它任务。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28.1pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">第五节 学生公寓服务中心卫生管理岗位职责</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">第一条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>负责公寓内的公共防疫、消杀工作。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">第二条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>监督、检查学生公寓公区卫生。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">第三条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>公寓服务中心公众平台日常维护与管理，平台通知、新闻的编辑。对于学生反映的问题、投诉等及时上报，回复处理结果等工作。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">第四条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>公寓中心新闻、报道的编辑。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">第五条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>负责所辖区域的物业维护维修、环境卫生、消防、纪律的检查、上报等管理工作，对辖区内出现的重大安全事件、公物损坏事件进行上报，积极配合调查处理。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">第六条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>负责辖区域的管理员的培训和管理工作，对管理员的工作进行检查、绩效考核，如发现问题，及时上报和处理。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">第七条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>汇总、整理、统计、保存和上报辖区的各项工作资料。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">第八条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>关注学生思想动态，公寓内有任何突发事件及时上报，积极参与处理。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">第九条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>完成学生公寓服务中心主任交办的其它任务。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28.1pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\">第六节<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>学生公寓服务中心资产管理岗位职责</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">第一条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>负责公寓服务中心国有资产的管理。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">第二条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>负责提交公寓物资采购计划。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">第三条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>负责公寓卫生保洁物品、办公用品的入库、出库。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">第四条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>保管好库房物资、不私自占用公物。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">第五条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>负责所辖区域的物业维护维修、环境卫生、消防、纪律的检查、上报等管理工作，对辖区内出现的重大安全事件、公物损坏事件进行调查、协助处理；对突发事件的上报与处理。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">第六条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>负责本片区区域的管理员的思想动态，并对管理员的工作进行检查、监督，发现问题，及时上报和处理。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">第七条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>汇总、整理、统计、保存和上报辖区的各项工作资料。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">第八条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>处理突发事件，关注负责辖区内学生及员工的动态。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">第九条<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>完成学生公寓服务中心主任交办的其它任务。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 9.9pt; text-indent: 28.1pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n宋体\">第七节<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">学生公寓服务中心质量监督考核管理岗位职责<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 9.9pt; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">第一条 负责学生寝室卫生评比数据录入，大型维修项目的立项和申报。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 9.9pt; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">第二条 负责员工值班排班安排，填报加班表。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 9.9pt; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">第三条 教师签到录入、担任公寓服务中心兼职档案员，负责所有文件、材料及各种活动成果的存档与保管。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 9.9pt; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">第四条 职工数据录入、统计，每学期流动人口登记、上报。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 9.9pt; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">第五条 用水数据的存档<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 9.9pt; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">第六条 负责中心档案管理工作。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 9.9pt; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">第七条 协助其它数据的录入，数据汇总。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 9.9pt; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">第八条 负责所辖区域的物业维护维修、环境卫生、消防、纪律的检查、上报等管理工作，对辖区内出现的重大安全事件、公物损坏事件进行调查处理并承担相应责任。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 9.9pt; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">第九条 负责辖区域的管理员的日常教育、培训和管理工作，并对管理员的工作进行检查、评比，发现问题，及时上报和处理。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 9.9pt; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">第十条 汇总、整理、统计、保存和上报辖区的各项工作资料。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 9.9pt; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">第十一条 处理突发事件，关注负责辖区内学生及员工的动态。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 9.9pt; text-indent: 28pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">第十二第 完成学生公寓服务中心主任交办的其它任务。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p></h1>\r\n                            \r\n                            \r\n                            \r\n                            \r\n                            \r\n                            ');
INSERT INTO `officeduty` VALUES ('14', '\r\n                                <p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\"><font size=\"5\"><b>物业服务中心工作职责</b></font></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 等线; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">物业</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">服务</span><span style=\"font-family: 等线; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">中心隶属于</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">后勤管理处</span><span style=\"font-family: 等线; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">，现有职工</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">85</span><span style=\"font-family: 等线; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">人，</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">包含室内外环境卫生、污水处理站、锅炉房、学校后勤库房四个主要分支，</span><span style=\"font-family: 等线; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">主要负责校园环境管理以及卫生保洁</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">、校园污水处理</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、水电气收费、物资管理发放、</span><span style=\"font-family: 等线; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">师生洗浴、开水供应等服务性保障工作。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">物业服务</span><span style=\"font-family: 等线; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">中心坚持以“始于师生需求，至于师生满意“为工作宗旨，高标准、高质量完成每一项工作任务，有效保障教学，科研以及师生的工作生活。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:20.85pt;mso-char-indent-count:1.49\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">具体工作分类及内容如下：</span><span style=\"font-family: 等线; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">　</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:22.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm;mso-char-indent-count:0\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">一、室内外环境卫生</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、室内外环境卫生清扫；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、室内卫生间清扫保洁；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、教学楼教室清扫保洁；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、校领导办公室清扫保洁；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、室外公共厕所清扫保洁；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、室外各垃圾房清理保洁；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、室内外垃圾箱清理保洁；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、室外各垃圾房处固体废物（非生活垃圾、非建筑垃圾）清运；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、各喷泉水池水面杂物打捞；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、重大活动道路、场馆冲洗。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm;mso-char-indent-count:0\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">二、污水处理厂</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、生活污水处理；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、污水处理站运行管理；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、篮球场污水泵站管理；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、绿化用中水泵送；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、污水泵站设备维护、保养；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、对口联系环保部门。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、联系环卫处，负责垃圾清运费的交纳。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm;mso-char-indent-count:0\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">三、澡水、开水房</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、澡水、开水房的运行管理；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、洗浴间管道设施维修；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、开水房设备维护、保养；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、空气能热泵维修、保养；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、保障学生开水、澡水及时供应。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm;mso-char-indent-count:0\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">四、水、电、气</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、校内各高压电缆分支箱维护、管理；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、校内高压开关维护、管理；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、校内</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">座变电站运行、维修、保养、管理；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、校内</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">800</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">吨储水池清洁、管理；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、水厂供学校三座总阀门井管理运行；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、校内停水、停电通知发布；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、全校水电费支付、水电费收缴；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、校内公共场所水电表抄录、统计；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、住宅区水电表抄录、收费；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、水厂、电力公司办理各类手续；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、自来水水质检测公示；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、联系水厂、电力公司；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、各施工单位水电费抄表、统计、收缴；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">14</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、校内各商业网点水电费抄表、统计、收纳；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、安信物业水电费管理、收费（对安信物业总水电表计量收费）；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">16</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、校内各食堂、网点煤气抄表、收费；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、与煤气公司结算煤气费；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、校内公共场所煤气设施报修。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm;mso-char-indent-count:0\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">五、电梯维保、电梯安全管理</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、负责联系维保公司对电梯及时维修保养；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、整理、归纳、保存电梯相关资料。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm;mso-char-indent-count:0\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">六、物资仓库管理</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、收货：对入库物资进行接货、验收、办理入库手续；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、保管：物资按指定位置进行堆码、保管、检查；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、发货：根据各部门开列物资领用单进行发货；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、盘点：每月对库存物资进行盘点，对库存情况上报；</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 14pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">5</span><span style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体;\">、工具管理：做好领用工具登记。</span></p>\r\n                            ');
INSERT INTO `officeduty` VALUES ('15', '\r\n                                <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt;font-family:黑体\">膳食科工作职责</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:30.0pt;line-height:25.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:\r\nexactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:仿宋\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:仿宋\">、负责全校食堂、餐饮网点、超市及校园商店的管理，确保其工作的正常运行。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:30.0pt;line-height:25.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:\r\nexactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:仿宋\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:仿宋\">、负责食堂及其他餐饮单位的食品卫生、饭菜质量、服务质量的管理。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:30.0pt;line-height:25.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:\r\nexactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:仿宋\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:仿宋\">、负责校内食品安全及生产安全管理，杜绝食物中毒事故的发生。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:30.0pt;line-height:25.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:\r\nexactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:仿宋\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:仿宋\">、负责食堂大宗物资采购的监督管理、食堂维修改造及农校对接工作。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:30.0pt;line-height:25.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:\r\nexactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:仿宋\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:仿宋\">、负责全校餐饮从业人员的健康检查、业务培训和组织协调工作。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:30.0pt;line-height:25.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:\r\nexactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:仿宋\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:仿宋\">、负责每日对食堂采购、加工、销售及餐具消洗等各环节的巡检和登记，问题整改及落实工作。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:30.0pt;line-height:25.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:\r\nexactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:仿宋\">7</span><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:仿宋\">、指导各食堂建立健全和完善各项规章制度。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:30.0pt;line-height:25.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:\r\nexactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:仿宋\">8</span><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:仿宋\">、做好售饭系统的故障申报及协调工作，确保售饭系统的正常运行。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:30.0pt;line-height:25.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:\r\nexactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:仿宋\">9</span><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:仿宋\">、严格执行有关财务制度，确保资金安全，做好各种账目、汇表的统计、核算工作。并及时向上级领导汇报食堂生产、经营状况。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:30.0pt;line-height:25.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:\r\nexactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:仿宋\">10</span><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:仿宋\">、建立师生投诉渠道，指导伙管会、饮食与健康协会做好各项日常工作。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:30.0pt;line-height:25.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:\r\nexactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:仿宋\">11</span><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:仿宋\">、负责美食节等大型餐饮活动的组织和承办工作。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:30.0pt;line-height:25.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:\r\nexactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:仿宋\">12</span><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:仿宋\">、配合食药监局，做好校内食品安全检查工作。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18.0pt;font-family:黑体\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-left:189.0pt;mso-para-margin-left:\r\n18.0gd;text-align:center;line-height:25.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:仿宋\">后勤管理处膳食科<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:25.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:仿宋\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n                            ');
INSERT INTO `officeduty` VALUES ('16', '\r\n                                \r\n                                \r\n                                \r\n                                <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nmajor-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:major-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:major-fareast\">校园管理科工作职责<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast\">一、负责校园的维修维护、装饰装修、基建改造工作。为保障学校教学科研工作的正常开展，根据学校的修缮计划，对单位工程的用途、使用要求等，征求有关部门的意见，并参与施工方案或设计图纸的研究、论证工作，办理项目立项、组织项目实施、验收移交工作。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast\">二、负责校园防洪抢险工作。制定年度防洪预案、安排防洪值班、组织防洪抢险。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast\">三、负责校园园林绿化规划、计划、实施和养护管理工作。校园力求做到净化、绿化和美化。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast\">四、完成处内交办的其他工作。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast\">学院维修统一报修电话<span lang=\"EN-US\">:<o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast\">0812--3373606</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast\">（上午<span lang=\"EN-US\">8:00--12:00</span>；下午<span lang=\"EN-US\">15:00--18:00</span>）；<span lang=\"EN-US\">0812--3500568</span>（中午<span lang=\"EN-US\">12:00--15:00</span>；晚上<span lang=\"EN-US\">18:00-8:00</span>）<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/logistics/image/news/35fcd.jpg\" width=\"auto\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\">报修微信二维码</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">校园管理科办公室电话：<span lang=\"EN-US\">0812-3500519<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n                            \r\n                            \r\n                            \r\n                            ');

-- ----------------------------
-- Table structure for policy
-- ----------------------------
DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `policy`;
CREATE TABLE `policy` (
  `policy_id` int(10) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `title` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `content` text NOT NULL,
  `time` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `path` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `level_id` int(10) NOT NULL,
  `approval` int(10) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `importance` int(10) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`policy_id`),
  UNIQUE KEY `PK_Policy` (`policy_id`),
  KEY `FK_Policy_level` (`level_id`),
  CONSTRAINT `policy_ibfk_1` FOREIGN KEY (`level_id`) REFERENCES `level` (`level_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=2 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

-- ----------------------------
-- Records of policy
-- ----------------------------
INSERT INTO `policy` VALUES ('1', '学生公寓管理制度', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">前　言<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:26.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:26.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">为贯彻落实“以人为本”的科学发展观，努力践行“三个代表”重要思想，坚持管理育人、服务育人、环境育人的宗旨，加强学生公寓管理，维护学生正常的学习、生活秩序，促进学生公寓文化建设，将学生公寓建设成为思想政治工作和素质教育的重要阵地，使其成为学生“温馨舒适的家园、强身益智的乐园、学习创新的摇篮”。<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:26.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">在长期的公寓管理实践中，学院和后勤管理处及学生公寓服务中心形成了正确的工作思路，逐步建立健全了一系列管理规章制度，为维护正常教育教学秩序和生活秩序，保障学生身心健康，促进学生德、智、体、美全面发展，确保学校全面、协调、可持续发展起到了重要的作用。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:26.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">为加强学生公寓服务中心正规化管理，强化员工的服务意识，端正工作作风，使各项工作有章可循、有据可依。我们汇集相关法规、制度和指南方面的内容，特制定本《管理制度》。学生公寓服务中心全体员工应根据工作分工，加强对本管理制度的学习和领会，认真履行本管理制度中的各项规定、岗位职责，并严格加以实施。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:26.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">学生公寓服务中心各职能部门应按照本《管理制度》对所属员工加以管理和考核，违反本管理制度将予以相应处罚。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:26.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">不尽之处，学生公寓服务中心将适时予以补充和完善。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:26.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">本《管理制度》从下发之日起执行。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>', '2019-02-26 10:12:37', 'file/rule/36e59_学生公寓管理制度.doc', '3', '0', '0');

